about.summary: Implements dictionaries that can be used in the 'SemNetCleaner' package. Also includes several functions aimed at facilitating the text cleaning analysis in the 'SemNetCleaner' package. This package is designed to integrate and update word lists and dictionaries based on each user's individual needs by allowing users to store and save their own dictionaries. Dictionaries can be added to the 'SemNetDictionaries' package by submitting user-defined dictionaries to <https://github.com/AlexChristensen/SemNetDictionaries>.

raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.1.6' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-semnetdictionaries
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/SemNetDictionaries_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/SemNetDictionaries/SemNetDictionaries_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1941ab96419b9488d7c90be60fc440d815326d1435265fd2a0127982d9a2cce6

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('SemNetDictionaries')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('SemNetDictionaries')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/AlexChristensen/SemNetDictionaries
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  summary: Implements dictionaries that can be used in the 'SemNetCleaner' package. Also includes
    several functions aimed at facilitating the text cleaning analysis in the 'SemNetCleaner'
    package. This package is designed to integrate and update word lists and dictionaries
    based on each user's individual needs by allowing users to store and save their
    own dictionaries. Dictionaries can be added to the 'SemNetDictionaries' package
    by submitting user-defined dictionaries to <https://github.com/AlexChristensen/SemNetDictionaries>.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - blankenberg
